sequenceDiagram
    participant T as Teacher
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as REST API
    participant Q as BullMQ
    participant W as AI Worker
    participant AI as AI Provider
    participant D as PostgreSQL

    Note over T,D: Phase 3 — Subscription Payment (Future)
    T->>FE: Select subscription plan
    FE->>API: POST /billing/checkout
    API->>API: Create Stripe Checkout Session
    API-->>FE: Redirect URL
    FE->>T: Redirect to Stripe Hosted Checkout
    T->>T: Complete payment on Stripe

    Note over T,D: Webhook Processing
    AI->>API: POST /webhooks/stripe (payment_intent.succeeded)
    API->>API: Verify signature
    API->>Q: Enqueue process_payment_webhook
    API-->>AI: 200 OK
    Q->>W: Consume job
    W->>D: Update subscription status
    W->>D: INSERT audit_log

    Note over T,D: Confirmation
    FE->>API: GET /billing/subscription
    API->>D: SELECT subscription
    API-->>FE: Active subscription
    FE->>T: Show confirmation
